precis:
Amendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (Schedule No. 896) providing
for use of polysorbate 80 in liquid smoke flavour concentrate and for the
addition of this concentrate to preserved meat products, prepared fish
products and preserved poultry meat products.
